# Branching And Ticket Linkage

- Start each feature or bugfix on a new branch linked to a Linear issue; prefer
  a **git worktree** per `.cursor/skills/git-worktrees/SKILL.md` so the primary
  checkout stays clean.
- Use branch naming with ticket prefix (for example `ENG-123-feature-name`).
- Include the ticket link in PRs and implementation summaries.
- Never update or merge `master` without explicit user permission.
